Introduction


Snowbaby (스노우베이비) is a Taiwanese YouTuber, influencer and actress. She is best known in South Korea as a former contestant on Mnet's reality survival show, Idol School. Snowbaby is half Taiwanese through her father, and mixed Uzbek and Tibetan through her mother.
